show.description: Thappuku thandanai - athukku innoru thappu panratha? intha kadhai la oru sila aniyaayangalukku niyaayan thedi tharradhu oru pei ah ? illa nijamaana manushana? pala swarasyangalum kadhai la pala twist'umm iruku. So fulla ah "The Dark Knight" ah kelunga.
